# My App

This is my capstone app, its made based on the anime Gundam and its hobby of model building. 

## Link to frontend repo
https://github.com/Henryp2995/Pena-Henry-Capstone-Frontend

## Dependencies

express: ^4.18.2
nodemon: ^3.0.3
mongoose: ^8.1.3

## Configuration

Ensure you have configured the following environment variables or values in a config.js file located in the root directory of the backend

## Usage

1. Clone this repository.
2. Run nodemon

## Endpoints

GET /
Description: Returns a welcome message.
Body: "Welcome to my webstore"

GET /gundams
Description: Retrieves all Gundam data.

POST /gundams
Description: allows you add a new gundam item


